Scary - +1d4 Intimidate, -1d4 Persuasion
Listener - +2 WIS, -2 STR
Elusive - +1d4 Stealth, disadv. on checks to get attention
Flighty - +2 INT, -2 WIS
Hurricane - +2 STR, -2 CON
Unseen - adv. on Initiative when you ambush someone
Spotlight - Hair/clothes tossed by wind, voice carries far, echoes loudly

